quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  75,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  75,1,Laaa uqsimu bi yawmil qiyaamah
  75,2,Wa laaa uqsimu bin nafsil lawwaamah
  75,3,Ayahsabul insaanu al lan najm'a 'izaamah
  75,4,Balaa qaadireena 'alaaa an nusawwiya banaanah
  75,5,Bal yureedul insaanu liyafjura amaamah
  75,6,Yas'alu ayyyaana yawmul qiyaamah
  75,7,Fa izaa bariqal basar
  75,8,We khasafal qamar
  75,9,Wa jumi'ash shamusu wal qamar
  75,10,Yaqoolul insaanu yaw ma 'izin aynal mafarr
  75,11,Kallaa laa wazar
  75,12,Ilaa rabbika yawma 'izinil mustaqarr
  75,13,Yunabba 'ul insaanu yawma 'izim bimaa qaddama wa akhkhar
  75,14,Balil insaanu 'alaa nafsihee baseerah
  75,15,Wa law alqaa ma'aazeerah
  75,16,Laa tuharrik bihee lisaa naka lita'jala bih
  75,17,Inna 'alainaa jam'ahoo wa qur aanah
  75,18,Fa izaa qaraanaahu fattabi' qur aanah
  75,19,Summa inna 'alainaa bayaanah
  75,20,Kallaa bal tuhibboonal 'aajilah
  75,21,Wa tazaroonal Aakhirah
  75,22,Wujoohuny yawma 'izin naadirah
  75,23,Ilaa rabbihaa naazirah
  75,24,Wa wujoohuny yawma 'izim baasirah
  75,25,Tazunnu any yuf'ala bihaa faaqirah
  75,26,Kallaaa izaa balaghatit taraaqee
  75,27,Wa qeela man raaq
  75,28,Wa zanna annahul firaaq
  75,29,Waltaffatis saaqu bissaaq
  75,30,Ilaa rabbika yawma'izinil masaaq
  75,31,Falaa saddaqa wa laa sallaa
  75,32,Wa laakin kazzaba wa tawalla
  75,33,Summa zahaba ilaaa ahlihee yatamatta
  75,34,Awlaa laka fa awlaa
  75,35,Summa awlaa laka fa awla
  75,36,Ayahsabul insaanu anyytraka sudaa
  75,37,Alam yaku nutfatam mim maniyyiny yumnaa
  75,38,Summa kaana 'alaqata fakhalaq fasawwaa
  75,39,Faja'ala minhuz zawjayniz zakara wal unsaa
  75,40,Alaisa zaalika biqaadirin 'alaaa any yuhyiyal mawtaa
